{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2bec2206bf","title":"给林希翎的信","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"170195412c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":8,"articleId":"2bec2206bf"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"},{"id":"fca195d890","name":"刘乃炎"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ba7cb04fb9","type":"title","text":"给林希翎的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"897edfe09c","type":"authors","text":"南开大学刘乃炎","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"bbb2400682","type":"subtitle","text":"[刘乃炎：南开大学化学系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"66c7e8f868","type":"appellation","text":"海果同学：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"bd9e5f7b49","type":"paragraph","text":"本来早已慕名，但详细一点情况，还是最近谭天荣、刘奇弟等来我校才知道的，现在先让我介绍一下自己，我叫刘乃炎，北京人，非团员，肃反中曾被斗过（原因是一批信，他们认为与胡风同调），肃反后承蒙校方屡次教导，然至今仍未改悔，确孺子不可教也，缘在我天生就是一种“谬论”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"2d33337cc5","type":"paragraph","text":"现在“是时候了”，我愿执着正义的火炬跑在前面，但我校的顽固势力相当强，那些长着硬壳的幸运儿和卫道者们用种种方法对民主力量进行反扑，还更有一种可卑的人，他们为争宠主子，不悼自己为众人所唾弃，这次谭刘等来我校就受到一些刁难和攻击，但最后我们毕竟胜利了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"fcb27a8f7a","type":"paragraph","text":"因为我校很多人还处于沉睡状态，需要激素，对你，我们是一向钦佩的，所以很希望你能来津到我校做一次讲演，我们将给你准备一切条件。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"e9ab1f6526","type":"paragraph","text":"另外，施建伟对我讲已给你去一信，不知可收到，最后希望能回信，可能的话告诉我来津日期，以便做一些准备工作。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"5e245c7269","type":"paragraph","text":"我的通信地址是南开大学第三宿舍215室，刘乃炎。如来津直接找我即可，同时就可找到各系的其它同学了。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"dc76e07994","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"d7bd194999","type":"appellation","text":"安好","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"},{"id":"fd5d7213ef","type":"paragraph","text":" 刘乃炎草6、8","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf"}],"page":{"id":"85f677c311","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bec2206bf","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}